```

> What 'verilator --version' are you using?  Did you try it with the git master version?
```  
$ verilator --version
Verilator 5.020 2024-01-01 rev UNKNOWN.REV
```
> What OS and distribution are you using?

I'm running this on Arch Linux with kernel 6.6.11-1-lts

> May we assist you in trying to fix this in Verilator yourself?

I don't think I have the skills to do that :sweat_smile:

Is this in fact unexpected behaviour? Thank you so much in advance!
